Mom 70th Birthday Number 70 Photo Collage Card It’s a great choice Mom 70th Birthday Number 70 Photo Collage Card There are many featuresPersonalize this big 70th birthday card with up to 13 different photographs. Designed for Mom (although Mom can be edited to a name or whatever you want), the number 70 photo collage is a thoughtful way to give a birthday card with a unique and special quality. The template is set up for you to easily create your own photo collage by adding your photos in order, starting from the top of each number. Change your pics around as often as you want until you get them all in the best spots. Inside the card there is another big number 70 and the option for you to add your own custom message.
